This paper is about the generalization performance of gradient descent for learning over-parameterized deep neural networks. The most relevant sub-category is likely cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the paper deals with theoretical analysis of learning algorithms. Other relevant sub-categories include cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as the paper deals with deep neural networks and their training.
